The question refers to the **group testing problem**, specifically the **combinatorial group testing** task of identifying defective items in a set using minimal tests.

\boxed{\text{Combinatorial group testing}}

This approach was originally improved by Virginia Williams (2011) and later re-derived using group-theoretic methods by Cohn, Kleinberg, Szegedy, and Umans. The focus is on efficiently identifying defective items with minimal queries.
